WEBVTT

00:00:01.967 --> 00:00:07.375
This Spirit when it manifests
it also gives you a state

00:00:07.455 --> 00:00:09.904
which we call as collective consciousness.

00:00:09.984 --> 00:00:14.394
It's the state by which you become,
– again I say become

00:00:14.474 --> 00:00:16.987
- it's actualization, it is not just talking -

00:00:17.067 --> 00:00:19.276
you become conscious collectively.

00:00:19.356 --> 00:00:22.652
Means you become conscious
of another person's centres

00:00:22.732 --> 00:00:24.368
on your fingertips.

00:00:24.474 --> 00:00:27.446
You also become self aware,

00:00:27.566 --> 00:00:28.944
you know about yourself,

00:00:29.024 --> 00:00:31.980
what centres are catching, where are we going.

00:00:32.100 --> 00:00:35.739
Like a person who becomes mentally upset,

00:00:35.859 --> 00:00:38.621
he doesn’t know, till he becomes mad,

00:00:38.701 --> 00:00:42.135
goes to lunatic asylum and dies, he does not know.

00:00:42.255 --> 00:00:45.235
But in Sahaja Yoga, immediately you can find out

00:00:45.315 --> 00:00:47.929
that there’s something going
wrong with your mental side.

00:00:48.909 --> 00:00:50.663
If a person gets into cancer,

00:00:50.743 --> 00:00:55.790
he might get into the state of
galloping cancer, about to die,

00:00:55.871 --> 00:00:58.230
then he may discover that he has got cancer.

00:00:58.311 --> 00:01:00.588
But in Sahaja Yoga if there’s a little imbalance,

00:01:00.669 --> 00:01:02.516
immediately it shows on your fingertips,

00:01:02.597 --> 00:01:10.491
and if you know how to do it, how to correct it,
then every problem is solved.

00:01:10.611 --> 00:01:14.144
So as I told you yesterday,
yoga has double meaning.

00:01:14.264 --> 00:01:17.315
Yoga means 'union with the Divine', that’s one.

00:01:17.435 --> 00:01:20.081
And the second one is the expertise,

00:01:20.161 --> 00:01:22.973
the deftness, what you
call in Sanskrit 'kaushalam'.

00:01:23.055 --> 00:01:24.621
You must have the deftness

00:01:24.701 --> 00:01:28.600
how to handle this all-pervading power
that is flowing through us,

00:01:28.720 --> 00:01:32.020
how to understand ourselves,
how to understand others,

00:01:32.100 --> 00:01:36.311
that’s an important part of Sahaja Yoga.

00:01:36.431 --> 00:01:39.976
First of all a little light is enlightened.

00:01:40.096 --> 00:01:42.976
You get the experience
of the Spirit to begin with.

00:01:43.091 --> 00:01:44.811
It's an actualization.

00:01:44.894 --> 00:01:47.505
But, then you must make it grow.

00:01:47.625 --> 00:01:50.527
Christ has given beautiful parables

00:01:50.621 --> 00:01:53.185
explaining this. The sprouting of the seeds

00:01:53.305 --> 00:01:55.834
which were thrown on the rocks.

00:01:55.954 --> 00:02:00.271
Some were thrown in the good soil
and some were neglected.

00:02:00.391 --> 00:02:02.951
And we find that everyday happening.

00:02:03.071 --> 00:02:05.860
Thousands come to my program and then I find

00:02:05.940 --> 00:02:07.940
some of them are lost in the rocks,

00:02:08.055 --> 00:02:10.070
some of them are wasted,

00:02:10.190 --> 00:02:12.864
but some of them become huge big trees

00:02:12.984 --> 00:02:16.296
to give shade, joy and support to others.

00:02:16.416 --> 00:02:18.056
We have to change this world.

00:02:18.136 --> 00:02:21.016
How are we going to change this world,
this horrible world,

00:02:21.099 --> 00:02:25.196
which is just on the precipice of destruction?

00:02:25.316 --> 00:02:28.156
The only way is that we have to change ourselves.

00:02:28.265 --> 00:02:31.325
That’s the transformation just waiting to happen.

00:02:31.445 --> 00:02:33.395
It's nothing that I am doing about it.

00:02:33.475 --> 00:02:35.941
I really tell you, I don’t do anything.

00:02:36.061 --> 00:02:39.415
I don’t do anything. Just waiting to get it.

00:02:39.495 --> 00:02:41.640
You just catch upon it and you get it.

00:02:41.720 --> 00:02:45.316
I may be just triggering it,
but you can trigger it also.

00:02:45.436 --> 00:02:49.715
So, one has to understand that
you have to be honest to yourself,

00:02:49.795 --> 00:02:51.459
you have to be fair to yourself.

00:02:51.539 --> 00:02:54.293
You have to understand your value.
You must know your worth,

00:02:54.373 --> 00:02:56.920
that you are a human being created

00:02:57.000 --> 00:03:00.476
out of small things like amoeba, from carbon,

00:03:00.596 --> 00:03:02.977
and today you are sitting here as human beings.

00:03:03.057 --> 00:03:04.977
You must be something very special.

00:03:05.057 --> 00:03:08.234
And this special thing has to become that thing

00:03:08.314 --> 00:03:10.971
which will make you understand what you are.

00:03:11.091 --> 00:03:13.131
Only thing, you are not yet connected.

00:03:13.240 --> 00:03:18.171
Only thing is that you have not yet felt
that divinity within you.

00:03:18.291 --> 00:03:20.820
We are all potentially divine.

00:03:20.940 --> 00:03:23.316
We have to just feel that divinity within us.

00:03:23.436 --> 00:03:27.500
But as a result of that, you are
such a powerful personality.

00:03:27.580 --> 00:03:29.370
Power of love.

00:03:29.490 --> 00:03:32.470
We have never used power of love.

00:03:32.590 --> 00:03:35.420
We have only used the power of hatred so far.

00:03:35.540 --> 00:03:39.127
Power of love is much above power of hatred.

00:03:39.207 --> 00:03:41.600
It can engulf all hatred.

00:03:41.680 --> 00:03:46.236
Can just suck in everything that is hatred.

00:03:46.316 --> 00:03:49.596
It’s very simple. Very
simple methods are to be put,

00:03:49.676 --> 00:03:52.596
only you must have desire to get transformed.

00:03:53.931 --> 00:03:57.251
Now the third thing that
happens with self realization

00:03:57.331 --> 00:04:04.091
is that you get a state of
peace, of bliss, and of joy.

00:04:06.090 --> 00:04:09.931
When the Kundalini rises
above this Agnya chakra

00:04:10.011 --> 00:04:12.864
you become thoughtlessly aware.

00:04:12.984 --> 00:04:16.326
It's called as 'nirvichar
samadhi'. Thoughtlessly aware,

00:04:16.406 --> 00:04:18.406
when there is no thought in your mind.

00:04:18.486 --> 00:04:20.506
If you want, you can think.

00:04:20.626 --> 00:04:22.956
If you want you can think,
but if you don’t want,

00:04:23.036 --> 00:04:25.625
you can be in that state where you don’t think.

00:04:25.745 --> 00:04:27.540
Actually, it’s maddening sometimes

00:04:27.660 --> 00:04:31.405
the way man is thinking
morning till evening,

00:04:31.525 --> 00:04:35.455
yarns after yarns, useless
things, a joyless pursuit.

00:04:35.575 --> 00:04:40.341
But when this thinking stops,
you are above the thoughts.

00:04:40.461 --> 00:04:43.621
I would say to give it a simile,

00:04:43.701 --> 00:04:47.295
that the waves of thought
come and go away.

00:04:47.415 --> 00:04:49.876
Another thought comes and goes away.

00:04:49.996 --> 00:04:54.036
We are jumping on the cusp
of the thought all the time.

00:04:54.156 --> 00:05:00.236
Supposing we can just get

00:05:00.356 --> 00:05:04.266
in the centre of the thought.

00:05:04.346 --> 00:05:06.782
That is the present.

00:05:06.902 --> 00:05:10.846
If we could stop at the present moment,

00:05:10.966 --> 00:05:13.282
then we are not worried about the thoughts.

00:05:13.402 --> 00:05:15.904
Like the waves of water, if you are in the waves

00:05:15.984 --> 00:05:17.544
you are frightened of that.

00:05:17.624 --> 00:05:19.775
But supposing you are in a boat

00:05:19.895 --> 00:05:23.570
then you can see the waves and enjoy them.

00:05:23.690 --> 00:05:26.040
In the same way, what happens to you,

00:05:26.160 --> 00:05:32.640
that you jump up to a higher state of existence

00:05:32.760 --> 00:05:37.510
through which you see the thoughts

00:05:37.630 --> 00:05:41.081
if you want, you don’t want to see, you can;
you need not see.

00:05:41.201 --> 00:05:46.516
Now the thoughts that you see also
are very wide and deeper

00:05:46.636 --> 00:05:48.476
where you get inspirations.

00:05:48.556 --> 00:05:51.276
That’s why, as Dr. Warren has told you,

00:05:51.356 --> 00:05:54.469
that your creativity improves.

00:05:54.550 --> 00:05:58.046
You can become tremendously dynamic.

00:05:58.166 --> 00:06:00.606
Because your time is not
wasted in wasteful things.

00:06:00.686 --> 00:06:03.086
You just know this is it.

00:06:03.166 --> 00:06:06.491
This is the exact. This is what we have to do.

00:06:06.611 --> 00:06:09.166
And that’s how people get rid of

00:06:09.246 --> 00:06:12.090
many of their problems of mental tensions.

00:06:12.210 --> 00:06:15.864
There’s no tension at all.
You don’t have any worries.

00:06:15.984 --> 00:06:19.111
You just see the thing like the witness.

00:06:19.231 --> 00:06:21.791
You become the witness of the whole drama.

00:06:21.871 --> 00:06:23.349
When you are in the drama,

00:06:23.429 --> 00:06:25.749
you think you are a part and parcel of the drama.

00:06:25.829 --> 00:06:28.075
Sometimes you weep with it and cry with it.

00:06:28.195 --> 00:06:31.525
But when the drama is over,
you realize it was just a drama:

00:06:31.605 --> 00:06:32.846
“I was not there”.

00:06:32.966 --> 00:06:34.646
In the same way it happens to you,

00:06:34.726 --> 00:06:37.216
that you achieve a witness state.

00:06:37.336 --> 00:06:41.331
It happens to you. Even if you want
to get involved, you cannot.

00:06:41.451 --> 00:06:42.977
You just cannot get it.

00:06:43.057 --> 00:06:45.294
That’s how you can solve the problems better

00:06:45.374 --> 00:06:47.196
because you are away from the problems.

00:06:47.276 --> 00:06:50.071
You can see what the problem is,
but when you are in it,

00:06:50.151 --> 00:06:54.186
you are upset, full of tension, worries,

00:06:54.306 --> 00:06:57.706
and sometimes people get so upset with it

00:06:57.815 --> 00:07:00.904
that they commit suicides
when they find no solution.

00:07:00.984 --> 00:07:02.664
But if you are away from it,

00:07:02.744 --> 00:07:07.026
then you can definitely solve the problem.

00:07:07.146 --> 00:07:09.786
Now this witness state has to grow within you

00:07:09.866 --> 00:07:14.950
gradually, with little understanding,
and with little meditation.